query:
SELECT 
  sm.id as manifestId,
  sm.manifestNumber,
  sm.totalOrders,
  smi.pickingOrderId,
  po.customerOrderNumber
FROM shipmentManifests sm
JOIN shipmentManifestItems smi ON smi.manifestId = sm.id
JOIN pickingOrders po ON po.id = smi.pickingOrderId
WHERE sm.manifestNumber = 'ROM-1769734935811';
